West_Palm_Beach.Westgate, Florida:
Westgate is an unincorporated census-designated place (CDP) in Palm Beach County, Florida, United States. The population was 7,975 at the 2010 census. Prior to then it was listed as the Westgate-Belvedere Homes CDP.


== Geography ==
Westgate is located at 26°41′57″N 80°5′40″W (26.699243, -80.094468).
